{
  "name": "RPlog_Attempted_Arrest",
  "title": "Attempted Arrest",
  "summary": "In Plaxton's Sandbar cantina on Caspar, the Caspian naval officer Lynae Cassius locates the wanted former Grand Moff Scaven Marx and sits to share a drink, philosophizing about genocide and orders while quietly cueing a security team. When Lynae signals the combat droid HM743 and her officers to move in for the arrest, Scaven draws his Kylan-3 blaster and resists, flipping a table and taking Lynae as a near-hostage as the bar erupts into chaos. The off-duty pilots Ruen, the winged Chyleni Kyrin Sh'vani, and Shael Winters, along with the agent Rasi, are swept into the brawl; Kyrin dives in and is gravely shot through one heart while Lynae is caught in the crossfire and Shael takes a sword wound. As the federal Constabulary under Captain Cunha surrounds the building and issues a single surrender warning, they breach with stun and gas grenades, knocking Scaven unconscious and neutralizing the melee. The constables arrest everyone bearing arms -- including Scaven and the Navy personnel involved -- leaving the Sandbar wrecked and its staff to clean up.",
